snippet.title: Batman: Arkham Asylum Joker Trailer
snippet.description: The high res video shows Batman battling some of his fiercest foes.  From the terrifying Killer Croc to the demented Joker, fans will get a glimpse into the macabre underworld of Gothams Arkham Asylum for the criminally insane.
